Wednesday, September 22, 1999

MERIT DOCKET

99-724. State ex rel. Graffi v. Horizon Freight Sys., Inc.

Franklin App. No. 98AP-71. On motion to dismiss. Motion to dismiss sustained. Cause dismissed.
